&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transformation Delivery Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a really exciting opportunity to be part of the Trust’s Operational Transformation Team and be responsible for effective planning, delivery and monitoring of projects sponsored and supported corporately through the and transformation programmes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have the opportunity to hold a key role in the Trust, driving the implementation of our existing transformation plans as well as further developing plans working in partnership with the other organisations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will support stakeholder engagement, reporting, planning and delivery of service reconfiguration, cost improvement plan realisation, and improvement projects across the Trust and in partnership with external stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warrington and Halton Teaching Hospitals - ‘WHH’ - are going places! &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These are challenging but exciting times for the NHS nationally, and for WHH in particular, but we believe there has never been a more exciting time to join our one great team - #TeamWHH!&lt;/p&gt;
